subject: Automobile Racing
Domestic Violence
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
Daytona 500 (Auto Race)
lead_paragraph: After a Delaware family court judge determined that Busch had choked his former girlfriend during a confrontation last September, Nascar suspended the Sprint Cup driver indefinitely.
